node.text:
Ready to sweat? Pilates blew my mind! Join me & Vic moving in a new way with Pilates!
.
You can visit her page her ➡️ @victoriapopoff 
.
She’s giving us a FREE month of virtual workouts with her if you use the code “JESSICA” at www.studioVtv.com
.
My outfit is from my upcoming athletic clothing line!! 😍 Can’t wait to share it with you!
.
Who wants more Pilates in their life? When would you go live with us to workout?
.
.
#virtualpilates
#studiovtv
#pilatesforanyone
